# 🛒 WooCommerce vs Aiswarya Sarees — Complete Gap Analysis

> **Project:** Aiswarya Sarees (Cast Prince)  
> **Tech Stack:** Next.js 16 + Supabase + WhatsApp API + Facebook Meta  
> **Date:** March 2, 2026

---

## 📊 Executive Summary

Your website is a **custom-built e-commerce storefront** with a strong WhatsApp integration and admin panel. However, compared to a full WooCommerce setup, there are **significant gaps** across shipping, payments, taxes, user accounts, and many standard e-commerce features.

| Area | Your Site | WooCommerce | Gap Level |
|------|-----------|-------------|-----------|
| Product Management | ✅ Basic | ✅ Advanced | 🟡 Medium |
| Order Management | ✅ Good | ✅ Advanced | 🟡 Medium |
| Shipping | ❌ Minimal | ✅ Full | 🔴 Critical |
| Payment Gateways | ❌ Basic (COD/UPI) | ✅ 100+ Gateways | 🔴 Critical |
| Tax System | ❌ Static field only | ✅ Dynamic/Auto | 🔴 Critical |
| User Accounts | ❌ None (customers) | ✅ Full | 🔴 Critical |
| Reviews & Ratings | ❌ None | ✅ Built-in | 🔴 Critical |
| Coupons & Discounts | ❌ None | ✅ Full | 🔴 Critical |
| Billing & Invoicing | 🟡 Partial | ✅ Full | 🟡 Medium |
| Privacy & GDPR | ❌ None | ✅ Built-in | 🔴 Critical |
| SEO & Analytics | ❌ Minimal | ✅ Full | 🟡 Medium |
| Email System | ❌ None | ✅ Full | 🔴 Critical |

---

## 1. 🏪 GENERAL / STORE SETTINGS

### ✅ What You HAVE
- Store name & description (Settings → General)
- Store status toggle (online/offline)
- Admin login/logout with session cookie
- Forgot password flow
- Admin sidebar navigation

### ❌ What's MISSING (WooCommerce Has)

| Feature | Description | Priority |
|---------|-------------|----------|
| **Multi-currency support** | Sell in different currencies (USD, EUR, GBP, etc.) | 🔴 High |
| **Timezone & date format settings** | Configurable date/time formats per region | 🟡 Medium |
| **Store address (used in invoices/shipping)** | Auto-populate invoices & calculate shipping | 🔴 High |
| **Measurement units** | Configurable weight (kg/lbs) and dimension (cm/in) units | 🟡 Medium |
| **Multiple admin roles** | Shop Manager, Editor, Customer roles with permissions | 🔴 High |
| **Activity log / Audit trail** | Track who made changes and when | 🟡 Medium |
| **Store notice / Maintenance mode** | Banner for announcements or maintenance | 🟢 Low |
| **Pagination settings** | Products per page, catalog ordering defaults | 🟢 Low |
| **Permalink / URL structure** | SEO-friendly product/category URLs | 🟡 Medium |
| **Settings actually save to database** | Your settings UI is static — nothing persists to Supabase | 🔴 Critical |

> [!CAUTION]
> Your Settings page is **purely cosmetic** — none of the values (GSTIN, shipping rates, business address) are saved to the database. They reset on page reload.

