## 2. 📦 PRODUCT MANAGEMENT

### ✅ What You HAVE
- Add/Edit/Delete products
- Product name, description, price, stock, image URL
- Category filtering (Silk, Cotton, Designer, etc.)
- Product groups/tags for broadcast targeting
- Table view & Card view toggle
- Search & sort (newest, low stock, high price)
- Copy product link & share to WhatsApp
- Facebook auto-post when adding product
- Stock level tracking
- Active/inactive product toggle

### ❌ What's MISSING (WooCommerce Has)

| Feature | Description | Priority |
|---------|-------------|----------|
| **Product variations/variants** | Size, color, material variants with separate prices/stock | 🔴 Critical |
| **Product attributes** | Fabric type, weave, weight, length, width as structured data | 🔴 Critical |
| **Multiple images / Gallery** | Multiple product photos with zoom, gallery slider | 🔴 Critical |
| **Image upload** | Currently only URL input — no direct file upload | 🔴 High |
| **Sale price / Discount price** | Scheduled sales with original vs sale price | 🔴 High |
| **SKU (Stock Keeping Unit)** | Unique product identifier for inventory | 🟡 Medium |
| **Product weight & dimensions** | Required for shipping calculations (length, width, height, weight) | 🔴 Critical |
| **Related products / Cross-sells** | "Customers also bought" recommendations | 🟡 Medium |
| **Upsells** | "You may also like" on product page | 🟡 Medium |
| **Product reviews & ratings** | Star ratings, written reviews by customers | 🔴 Critical |
| **Product visibility** | Catalog visibility, search visibility, featured products | 🟡 Medium |
| **Virtual / Downloadable products** | Digital goods with download links | 🟢 Low |
| **Inventory management** | Low stock threshold, backorder settings, stock status | 🟡 Medium |
| **Bulk edit / Import-Export** | CSV import/export for products | 🟡 Medium |
| **Product sorting on frontend** | Sort by price, popularity, rating, date | 🟡 Medium |
| **Wishlist** | Save products for later | 🟡 Medium |
| **Compare products** | Side-by-side product comparison | 🟢 Low |
| **Product page (dedicated)** | Individual SEO-friendly product detail page with URL | 🔴 Critical |
| **Breadcrumb navigation** | Home > Category > Product navigation | 🟡 Medium |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Your products have **no weight, dimensions, or SKU** — these are essential for calculating shipping costs. WooCommerce requires these fields per product.

