## 3. 🚚 SHIPPING

### ✅ What You HAVE
- Flat shipping rate display (₹99)
- Free shipping above ₹2000 (hardcoded in shop page)
- Delivery partner name field (UI only, not saved)
- Estimated delivery time field (UI only, not saved)
- Delivery address collected at checkout

### ❌ What's MISSING (WooCommerce Has)

| Feature | Description | Priority |
|---------|-------------|----------|
| **Shipping Zones** | Define geographic zones (North India, South India, International) | 🔴 Critical |
| **Shipping by location** | Different rates per state/country/pincode | 🔴 Critical |
| **Shipping by weight** | Rate calculated based on product weight (e.g., ₹50/kg) | 🔴 Critical |
| **Shipping by dimensions** | Rate based on package length × width × height | 🔴 High |
| **Multiple shipping methods** | Standard, Express, Same-day, Pickup options | 🔴 Critical |
| **Shipping classes** | Group products by shipping cost (Heavy, Light, Fragile) | 🟡 Medium |
| **Flat rate per class** | Different flat rates per shipping class | 🟡 Medium |
| **Free shipping conditions** | Free shipping above X amount, or with coupon | 🟡 Medium |
| **Local pickup** | In-store pickup option | 🟢 Low |
| **Shipping calculator** | Real-time shipping cost estimate on cart page | 🔴 High |
| **Shipping carrier integration** | DTDC, BlueDart, Delhivery, Shiprocket API integration | 🔴 Critical |
| **Tracking number** | Per-order tracking number with carrier link | 🔴 Critical |
| **Shipping label generation** | Auto-generate shipping labels with barcodes | 🟡 Medium |
| **Delivery date estimation** | Show estimated delivery date based on zone + method | 🟡 Medium |
| **Shipping restrictions** | Block certain products from specific zones/countries | 🟡 Medium |
| **International shipping** | Customs declarations, duties, HS codes | 🟢 Low |

> [!WARNING]
> Your shipping is **100% hardcoded** (`cartTotal >= 2000 ? 0 : 99`). There is no zone-based, weight-based, or dynamic shipping calculation. This is the biggest gap vs WooCommerce.

### WooCommerce Shipping Zone Example

```
Zone: Tamil Nadu (Local)
├── Free Shipping (above ₹2000)
├── Flat Rate: ₹50
└── Local Pickup: ₹0

Zone: Rest of India (Domestic)
├── Free Shipping (above ₹5000)  
├── Standard: ₹100
└── Express: ₹200

Zone: International
├── Flat Rate: ₹1500
└── Express: ₹3000
```

