## 4. 💳 PAYMENT METHODS

### ✅ What You HAVE
- COD (Cash on Delivery)
- UPI (basic — redirect to WhatsApp for confirmation)
- Payment method stored in order record

### ❌ What's MISSING (WooCommerce Has)

| Feature | Description | Priority |
|---------|-------------|----------|
| **Razorpay integration** | India's #1 payment gateway (Cards, UPI, NetBanking, Wallets) | 🔴 Critical |
| **Stripe integration** | International cards, Apple Pay, Google Pay | 🔴 High |
| **PayPal** | International payments | 🟡 Medium |
| **PhonePe / Google Pay QR** | Direct UPI payment with auto-verification | 🔴 High |
| **EMI options** | Monthly installment payments | 🟡 Medium |
| **Wallet (Paytm, etc.)** | Digital wallet integration | 🟡 Medium |
| **Net Banking** | Direct bank transfers | 🟡 Medium |
| **Bank transfer (NEFT/IMPS)** | Manual bank transfer with verification | 🟡 Medium |
| **Payment status tracking** | Pending → Processing → Completed → Refunded | 🔴 Critical |
| **Refund processing** | Full/partial refunds through payment gateway | 🔴 Critical |
| **Payment retry** | Failed payment retry mechanism | 🟡 Medium |
| **Saved payment methods** | Store card/UPI for repeat customers | 🟢 Low |
| **Payment gateway test mode** | Sandbox/test mode for development | 🟡 Medium |
| **Transaction ID storage** | Store gateway transaction references | 🔴 High |
| **Payment receipts** | Auto-generated payment confirmation | 🟡 Medium |

> [!CAUTION]
> You have **NO real payment gateway integration**. UPI is handled via WhatsApp chat (manual confirmation). There's no automated payment verification, no Razorpay, no Stripe.

