## 5. 🧾 BILLING & INVOICING

### ✅ What You HAVE
- PDF invoice generation (via jsPDF)
- Invoice storage in Supabase storage bucket
- Invoice list view in admin panel
- Invoice viewer modal with print support
- Order items listed on invoice
- Invoice URL stored per order

### ❌ What's MISSING (WooCommerce Has)

| Feature | Description | Priority |
|---------|-------------|----------|
| **Billing address (customer-side)** | Full billing address separate from shipping | 🔴 High |
| **Tax breakdown on invoice** | CGST, SGST, IGST itemized on invoice | 🔴 Critical |
| **Invoice numbering system** | Sequential invoice numbers (INV-001, INV-002) | 🟡 Medium |
| **Company details on invoice** | Registered business name, GSTIN, PAN auto-populated | 🔴 High |
| **Credit notes** | For refunds / returns | 🟡 Medium |
| **Proforma invoice** | Pre-payment invoice | 🟢 Low |
| **Invoice email attachment** | Auto-email invoice PDF to customer | 🔴 High |
| **Multi-tax invoice** | Different tax rates for different products | 🔴 High |
| **HSN/SAC codes** | Tax classification codes required by GST law | 🔴 High |
| **Billing history (customer-side)** | Customers can view their own invoices | 🟡 Medium |

