## 6. 💰 TAXES

### ✅ What You HAVE
- Default tax rate field in Settings (5%, UI only — not saved or applied)
- GSTIN number field (UI only — not saved)
- PAN number field (UI only — not saved)

### ❌ What's MISSING (WooCommerce Has)

| Feature | Description | Priority |
|---------|-------------|----------|
| **Tax calculation on orders** | Tax NOT actually calculated or added to order total | 🔴 Critical |
| **Tax rates by country/state** | Different GST rates for inter-state vs intra-state | 🔴 Critical |
| **CGST + SGST split** | Central GST + State GST for intra-state orders | 🔴 Critical |
| **IGST for inter-state** | Integrated GST for orders crossing state borders | 🔴 Critical |
| **Tax-inclusive vs exclusive pricing** | Option to show prices with or without tax | 🔴 High |
| **Tax per product category** | Different tax rates (5%, 12%, 18%) for different product types | 🔴 High |
| **Tax exemption** | Exempt certain products or customers from tax | 🟡 Medium |
| **Tax reports** | Tax collected summary for GST filing | 🔴 Critical |
| **HSN code per product** | Required for GST compliance in India | 🔴 High |
| **Tax display in cart/checkout** | Show tax breakdown before order placement | 🔴 High |
| **International tax (VAT/GST)** | Handle tax for international customers | 🟢 Low |
| **Tax class management** | Standard, Reduced, Zero-rate tax classes | 🟡 Medium |

> [!CAUTION]
> **Tax is completely non-functional.** The settings fields are cosmetic. No tax is calculated, no GSTIN appears on invoices, and no GST compliance exists. This is a **legal requirement** for Indian e-commerce.

