| **Coupon code input at checkout** | Apply discount codes | 🔴 Critical |
| **Tax display in checkout** | Show tax breakdown before placing order | 🔴 Critical |
| **Shipping method selection** | Choose between standard/express shipping | 🔴 Critical |
| **Shipping cost calculator** | Real-time shipping estimate based on address | 🔴 High |
