## 📋 PRIORITY IMPLEMENTATION ROADMAP

### 🔴 Phase 1 — Critical (Must Have for a Real E-commerce Store)

These are **legally or functionally essential** features:

```
1. ✅ Persist settings to database (Settings page)
2. 💳 Razorpay payment gateway integration  
3. 💰 Tax calculation (GST: CGST + SGST / IGST)
4. 🧾 Tax on invoices (HSN codes, GSTIN)
5. 🚚 Shipping zones & rate calculation
6. 🛒 Persistent cart (localStorage at minimum)
7. 👤 Customer accounts (register, login, my orders)
8. ⭐ Product reviews & ratings
9. 🏷️ Coupon/discount system
10. 📄 Privacy policy & Terms pages
11. 📦 Product weight & dimensions fields
12. 📧 Order confirmation emails
13. 🔙 Returns & refund processing
14. 📄 Individual product pages with SEO URLs
```

### 🟡 Phase 2 — Important (Standard E-commerce Expectations)

```
1. Product variants (size, color)
2. Multiple product images
3. Image upload (not just URL)
4. Shipping carrier integration (Shiprocket/Delhivery)
5. Tracking numbers per order
6. Sale price / scheduled sales
7. Abandoned cart recovery
8. Customer saved addresses
9. Google Analytics integration
10. Structured data (Schema.org)
11. XML Sitemap
12. SKU per product
13. State/country dropdown at checkout
14. Email field at checkout
15. Order export (CSV)
```

### 🟢 Phase 3 — Nice to Have (Competitive Advantage)

```
1. Wishlist
2. Product comparison
3. Multi-language
4. Blog/content
5. Social login
6. PWA / installable app
7. Advanced analytics dashboard
8. Loyalty points system
9. Gift cards
10. BOGO deals
```

